Not sure why
Open cmd
$ cd C:\
Navigate to (options):
$ cd C:\Users\USERNAME\AppData\Local\Continuum\Anaconda2\Scripts\anaconda.exe
$ cd C:\Users\USERNAME\AppData\Local\Continuum\Anaconda2\envs
$ cd C:\Users\USERNAME\AppData\Local\Continuum\Anaconda3\envs

